   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="right" type="letterhead"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3173_0010-1"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40583">Dessauerstrasse 19</rs></hi></hi></seg><dateline rend="left"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs>, <date when="1903-02-21">21. Februar</date>.</dateline><salute rend="center">Mein lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03364-1"/>willkommen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03364-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> kam am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="date-only" target="1903-02-22"/> morgens in
                     <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs> an.</note>! Ich muß leider zu
                  eine<unclear>r</unclear><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="latintype">Matinée</hi> ins <rs type="place" ref="#pmb42626">Re<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>idenztheater</rs> (»<hi rend="latintype"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb146870">Leonarda</rs></hi>« von <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2400">Björnson</rs></hi>). Anbei ein Billet, für den Fall, daß Du <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03364-2"/>mitkommen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03364-2"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> kam nicht mit, man sah sich am
                  Nachmittag, <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1903-02-22" subtype="cf"/>.</note> will<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t. Wenn nicht,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o <pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3173_0011-1"/>komme ich
                  zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen <time>3</time> und <del rend="strikethrough">1/</del><time>3 ½ Uhr</time> zu Dir ins <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb88">Hôtel</rs></hi>. Bis <time>5 Uhr</time> bin ich frei.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <lb/>Dein <lb/><signed>Paul Goldm</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
